org.pepstock.charba.client.data

Class AbstractCanvasObjectCallback<T extends CanvasObject>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.data.AbstractCanvasObjectCallback<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of canvas object
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ColorCallback<DatasetContext>, Scriptable<Object,DatasetContext>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DatasetGrandientCallback, DatasetPatternCallback

    abstract class AbstractCanvasObjectCallback<T extends CanvasObject>
extends Object
implements ColorCallback<DatasetContext>
    Callback to set a CanvasObject as background color.
    This is used and set in the data set when a canvas object is set for a background color.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
